<view class="page"><view class="example-info">数字输入框组件多用于购物车加减商品等场景</view><view class="example-title">基本用法</view><view class="example-body"><uni-number-box vue-id="1" bind:__l="__l"></uni-number-box></view><view class="example-title">设置最小值和最大值</view><view class="example-body"><uni-number-box vue-id="2" min="{{2}}" max="{{9}}" value="{{5}}" bind:__l="__l"></uni-number-box></view><view class="example-title">设置步长（步长0.1）</view><view class="example-body"><uni-number-box vue-id="3" step="{{0.1}}" bind:__l="__l"></uni-number-box></view><view class="example-title">禁用状态</view><view class="example-body"><uni-number-box vue-id="4" disabled="{{true}}" bind:__l="__l"></uni-number-box></view><view class="example-title">{{"获取输入的值 : "+numberValue}}</view><view class="example-body"><uni-number-box vue-id="5" value="{{numberValue}}" data-event-opts="{{[['^change',[['change']]]]}}" bind:change="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-number-box></view></view>